\par }{\fs24\lang2057 <#/>THE Deputy Prime Minister and Minister for Home Affairs, Augustine Mrema came under fire in Parliament this week, with one member of Parliament charging by implication that the minister was acting like Tanzania's High Court.
\par <#/>The Member of Parliament for Tarime, Kisyeri Chambiri, said at one time, the minister flew in a helicopter from Dar es Salaam to Kewanja (Nyangoto), a remote village in his constituency, 
