\par }{\fs24\lang2057 <I> <#/>}{\b\fs24\lang2057 <h> State House against prefabs </h>
\par }{\fs24\lang2057 <#/>The State House is opposed to the 44 billion/- National Provident Fund (NPF) plan to import prefabricated homes in Tanzania.
