/>Sometimes in the late 1980s some politicians from Zanzibar were also kicked out of CCM; all that in the name of fostering the union," the minister said.
\par <#/><ea/>Ndugu Khatib was cautious on the future of the Union and urged Tanzanians to be careful in charting out the path which would determine the destiny of the nation.
