international community would be laying a foundation for a peaceful and prosperous world for all <-/manking>.
\par <#/>He also expressed hope that the end of the }{\i\fs24\lang2057 Cold War}{\fs24\lang2057  would create a more conducive climate for the nations of the world to take collective acti
