\par <#/>Meanwhile, the ministry has been advised to transfer experts from other regions to the under\-staffed Lindi, Mtwara, Coast, Mara and Shinyanga regions.
\par <#/>It was the view of the conference also that the present distribution of livestock drug
s is weak and the drugs do not reach livestock keepers at the right moment for the fair price. <#/>It was noted that experts were also more interested in selling the drugs than giving service.
\par <#/>The conference resolved, therefore, that the ministry should devise a new system of distribution to ensure that the drugs reached the people.
